Package com.rockhoppertech.collections Description

Circular collection classes. There are many public open source projects that provide collections for Java. I could not find a simple Circular List. Therefore I made one. If you know of a simpler better made version, let me know.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Gene De Lisa
